Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是有點驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反而是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕自己會變得和以前不一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天有什麼想吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會加油做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這週開始打工的排班要增加了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事…請加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(500,500)\an7\fs40\c&H000000&}註：打工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}課已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天也要打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你果然是在生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氣我那次拒絕了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你一直躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙人 你絕對是在躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那為什麼突然打那麼多份工…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是…這麼晚還一個人在外面晃是我不夠謹慎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我太沒有防備了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一次見到我就這麼認為嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考試的時候一直在擔心成績能不能合格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 我才不會拜託其他人來輔導我功課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在不是想說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近都沒怎麼見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算我問你你也不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總感覺很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是你說得那麼輕描淡寫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是…想多和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你偷笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真 真是的 我不管了
